### Nadi API Sample Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### Get all sports
GET {{baseUrl}}/sports

### Search venues nearby
GET {{baseUrl}}/venues?lat=33.8938&lon=35.5018&radius=5000&sport=FOOTBALL&minPrice=10&maxPrice=50&players=4

### Get venue details
GET {{baseUrl}}/venues/64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0

### Check court availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/courts/64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d1/availability?date=2024-01-15

### Create hold reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/hold
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courtId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d1",
  "startTime": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-01-15T11:00:00Z",
  "userId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d2",
  "playersCount": 4
}

### Confirm reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d3/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d2"
}

### Cancel reservation
POST {{baseUrl}}/reservations/64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d3/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d2",
  "reason": "Change of plans"
}

### Get my reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations/my?userId=64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d2

### Owner: Create venue
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/venues
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "name": "Beirut Sports Center",
  "phone": "+961-1-234567",
  "address": "Hamra Street, Beirut",
  "latitude": 33.8938,
  "longitude": 35.5018
}

### Owner: Create court
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/courts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "venueId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0",
  "sportId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d4",
  "name": "Court 1",
  "surface": "Synthetic",
  "maxPlayers": 10
}

### Owner: Set pricing rules
POST {{baseUrl}}/owner/courts/64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d1/price-rules
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00",
  "pricePerSlot": 25.00
}

### Developer: Generate API key
POST {{baseUrl}}/developer/api-key
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "userId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d5",
  "rateLimit": 1000
}

### Developer: Rotate API key
POST {{baseUrl}}/developer/api-key/rotate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{developerToken}}

{
  "userId": "64f8a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d5",
  "oldKey": "ak_1234567890abcdef"
}

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@ownerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
@developerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
